#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000200005ADE"
msgid "On the table you see a bowl of water, a rough soap, and next to it a small hand mirror. A straight razor soaks inside the wash basin."
msgstr ""
"Auf dem Tisch siehst du eine Schüssel mit Wasser, grobe Seife und daneben einen kleinen Handspiegel. Im Waschbecken schwimmt ein Rasiermesser."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Physical Instrument
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700013409"
msgid "Yeah, purified yourself right back to infancy. You look like a baby!"
msgstr ""
"Ja, direkt zurück in die Kindheit gereinigt. Du siehst aus wie ein Baby!"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F0000F9FD"
msgid "[Leave.]"
msgstr ""
"[Ende.]"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F00013356"
msgid "How would you know? You haven't even seen your face! Go take a peek in the mirror, then decide for yourself."
msgstr ""
"Woher willst du das wissen? Du hast dein Gesicht noch nicht einmal gesehen! Geh zum Spiegel und urteile selbst."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Suggestion
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E125"
msgid "Your face, such as it is. A regular human face. Sans expression."
msgstr ""
"Dein Gesicht, so wie es ist. Ein normales menschliches Gesicht. Ohne den Blick."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Suggestion
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E136"
msgid "The beardless nature of your cheeks makes The Expression seem even more like a terrifying grimace."
msgstr ""
"Die bartlose Natur deiner Wangen lässt den Blick noch mehr wie eine schreckliche Grimasse wirken."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000DB17"
msgid "Time to shave. Get these mutton chops off."
msgstr ""
"Zeit für eine Rasur. Weg mit den Koteletten."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "tooltip1/0x0100005A0000DB17"
msgid "Dresscode: True man."
msgstr ""
"Dresscode: Echter Mann"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Composure
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0F4"
msgid "A fresh start looms ahead. Clean yourself up and be born anew."
msgstr ""
"Ein Neuanfang steht bevor. Wasch dich und sei wie neugeboren."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1E2"
msgid "The sharp blade chafes against your skin, producing a scratching sound. The surface underneath the beard feels tender, the air brushing against it chilly."
msgstr ""
"Die scharfe Klinge scheuert an deiner Haut und erzeugt ein kratzendes Geräusch. Die Oberfläche unter dem Bart fühlt sich zart an, als kühle Luft darüber streicht."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000070001225C"
msgid "But man persists and after fifteen minutes pass, you look almost presentable. Sort of. The sudden absence of the morbid dead tissue smell instantly lifts your spirit."
msgstr ""
"Doch der Mensch ist hartnäckig, und nach fünfzehn Minuten siehst du schon beinahe präsentabel aus. Einigermaßen. Das plötzliche Fehlen des widerlichen Geruchs von totem Gewebe versetzt dich sofort in bessere Stimmung."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700012282"
msgid "Scrubbing all the necrotic tissue off your hands takes a while. The fingernails are especially hard. Death has made it's way into every nook and cranny..."
msgstr ""
"Es dauert eine Weile, das nekrotische Gewebe von deinen Händen zu schrubben. Die Fingernägel sind besonders schwierig. Der Tod hat es geschafft, sich in jede Ritze zu zwängen."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F0000FA0B"
msgid "The water reflects back a vague image of your face -- nose bulbous and red, hair unkempt, wrinkles lining the eyes and forehead. The 'stache is gigantic."
msgstr ""
"Das Wasser reflektiert ein verschwommenes Bild von deinem Gesicht – eine Nase, knollig und rot, zerzaustes Haar, Falten um die Augen und auf der Stirn. Der Schnauzer ist gigantisch."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0E8"
msgid "I *need* to shave the chops!"
msgstr ""
"Ich <i>muss</i> die Koteletten abrasieren!"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Physical Instrument
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0EF"
msgid "You'll be lookin' like a pansy without the chops! A fuckin' pansy!"
msgstr ""
"Ohne die Koteletten wirst du wie ein Bubi aussehen! Ein verdammter Bubi!"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Volition
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1A8"
msgid "There's no way to salvage this."
msgstr ""
"Es gibt keine Möglichkeit, das jetzt noch zu retten."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000070001227C"
msgid "But man persists and finally your bruised hands look clean and presentable... sort of. The sudden absence of the morbid dead tissue smell is uplifting."
msgstr ""
"Doch der Mensch ist hartnäckig, und endlich sehen deine verletzten Hände sauber und präsentabel aus … Einigermaßen. Das plötzliche Fehlen des widerlichen Geruchs von totem Gewebe ist aufbauend."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0DD"
msgid "This isn't sharp enough. Scrape harder."
msgstr ""
"Das ist nicht scharf genug. Du kratzt härter."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0E2"
msgid "Stop, for crying out loud! You're gonna cut your own throat."
msgstr ""
"Stopp, verdammt noch mal! Du schlitzt dir noch die Kehle auf."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E113"
msgid "The water reflects back a vague image of your clean-shaven face. Despite the bulbous nose, unkempt hair and persistent swelling, you look... a little younger, maybe?"
msgstr ""
"Das Wasser reflektiert ein verschwommenes Bild von deinem frischrasierten Gesicht. Trotz der Knollennase, dem zerzausten Haar und der anhaltenden Schwellung siehst du … ein wenig jünger aus, vielleicht?"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700012221"
msgid "Leave it for now."
msgstr ""
"Lass es fürs Erste sein."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700012255"
msgid "Thank god you didn't go in there barehanded! Death smell is notoriously difficult to get off yourself and your clothes though and cleaning up takes a while..."
msgstr ""
"Zum Glück hast du die Sache nicht mit bloßen Händen angepackt! Es ist bekanntermaßen schwierig, den Geruch des Todes von sich und seiner Kleidung zu bekommen, und das Waschen dauert eine Weile …"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000DB2B"
msgid "Your hand trembles as you scratch at your cheek... oh no, that's not how a grown man shaves!"
msgstr ""
"Deine Hand zittert, als du dir über die Wange kratzt … Oh nein, so rasiert ein erwachsener Mann sich aber nicht!"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Interfacing
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000070001228F"
msgid "Should have used gloves. Detectives use gloves, when they go rummaging around in someone's dead brain..."
msgstr ""
"Hättest Handschuhe benutzen sollen. Detectives benutzen Handschuhe, wenn sie im Hirn eines Toten herumwühlen …"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E0D7"
msgid "They feel so smooth, surprisingly so. A feeling of freshness overcomes you, as if you just came from a cold bath."
msgstr ""
"Sie fühlen sich so erstaunlich glatt an. Ein Gefühl der Frische überkommt dich, als hättest du ein kaltes Bad genommen."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Volition
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000070001222F"
msgid "The centipede is exaggerating -- people don't actually cut their own throats when they're shaving. At least not accidentally."
msgstr ""
"Der Tausendfüßler übertreibt – Menschen schneiden sich nicht wirklich die Kehle auf, wenn sie sich rasieren. Zumindest nicht versehentlich."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1C7"
msgid "Beneath the doubt sprouts a new vigour, like you've discarded some bad decisions. It feels as though you've passed through a ritual. Emerged from cold water, even..."
msgstr ""
"Unter dem Zweifel entsteht eine neue Kraft, als hättest du einige schlechte Entscheidungen verworfen. Du fühlst dich, als ob du ein Ritual durchlaufen hättest. Als wärst du aus kaltem Wasser aufgetaucht …"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Esprit de Corps
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000200005AE4"
msgid "Please attend to personal hygiene on your own time."
msgstr ""
"Bitte kümmere dich in deiner Freizeit um deine Körperpflege."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1BD"
msgid "Feel your clean-shaven cheeks."
msgstr ""
"Du fährst dir über die glattrasierten Wangen."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1B8"
msgid "The razor lands with a *clang*. A red trickle begins to spread in the water."
msgstr ""
"Die Rasierklinge landet mit einem <i>Scheppern</i>. Ein rotes Rinnsal beginnt sich im Wasser auszubreiten."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Washbasin
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F0000F9F6"
msgid "On the table you see a bowl of water, a rough soap, and next to it a small hand mirror. A straight razor soaks inside the wash basin."
msgstr ""
"Auf dem Tisch siehst du eine Schüssel mit Wasser, grobe Seife und daneben einen kleinen Handspiegel. Im Waschbecken schwimmt ein Rasiermesser."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000200005AEC"
msgid "The lieutenant throws you an embarrassed glance as you consider the washbasin."
msgstr ""
"Der Lieutenant wirft dir einen verlegenen Blick zu, als du das Waschbecken betrachtest."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700012228"
msgid "Thank god, I would have cut your throat."
msgstr ""
"Gott sei Dank, ich hätte dir die Kehle aufgeschnitten."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002900001F19"
msgid "Is shaving the right call?"
msgstr ""
"Ist Rasieren die richtige Entscheidung?"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1AE"
msgid "Drop the razor in the water basin."
msgstr ""
"Du lässt die Rasierklinge ins Waschbecken fallen."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002900001F06"
msgid "Your hand shakes so hard you can't even muster up the courage to *try*. Maybe you're just too *wild* at heart?"
msgstr ""
"Deine Hand zittert so sehr, dass du nicht einmal den Mut dazu aufbringen kannst, es zu <i>versuchen</i>. Vielleicht bist du zu <i>wild</i> im Herzen?"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002900001F13"
msgid "*Was* shaving the right call?"
msgstr ""
"War Rasieren wirklich die richtige Entscheidung?"

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000DB25"
msgid "Like an artist with a brush or a master swordsman, you use the small mirror and the straight razor -- with some soap -- to remove all that unkempt hair from below the nose-line."
msgstr ""
"Du benutzt den kleinen Spiegel und die Rasierklinge wie ein Künstler seinen Pinsel oder ein Schwertmeister sein Schwert – mit etwas Seife – um all das ungepflegte Haar unter der Nasenlinie zu entfernen."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700012244"
msgid "Wash the smell of death off yourself."
msgstr ""
"Du wäschst dir den Geruch des Todes ab."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Alternate1/0x0100000700012244"
msgid "First wash the smell of death off yourself."
msgstr ""
"Du wäschst dir zuerst den Geruch des Todes ab."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Physical Instrument
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000700013401"
msgid "You don't have a face anymore. It's all baby-ass now."
msgstr ""
"Du hast kein Gesicht mehr. Das ist jetzt alles nur noch Babyarsch."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Logic
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E120"
msgid "You almost look like a professional."
msgstr ""
"Du siehst fast schon wie ein Profi aus."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1B3"
msgid "Your hand refuses to move another millimetre. A small trickle of blood runs down your cheek."
msgstr ""
"Deine Hand weigert sich, sich noch einen Millimeter zu bewegen. Ein kleines Rinnsal Blut läuft dir die Wange herunter."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Washbasin
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005A0000E1C2"
msgid "Hope this was the right decision."
msgstr ""
"Ich hoffe, es war die richtige Entscheidung."

#. Title = HQ / WASHBASIN
#. Description = A washbasin An interactable dialogue where you can shave your beard/muttonchops! This changes the portrait in the mirror dialogue, and the one on UI.
#. Actor = Hand/Eye Coordination
#. Conversant = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000950000028D"
msgid "The sharp blade chafes against your skin, producing a scratching sound. The surface underneath the beard feels tender, the air brushing against it chilly."
msgstr ""
"Die scharfe Klinge scheuert an deiner Haut und erzeugt ein kratzendes Geräusch. Die Oberfläche unter dem Bart fühlt sich zart an, als kühle Luft darüber streicht."
